quence as the experimental one for\n$Ce_{2}Au_{1-x}Co_{x}Si_{3}$, if $J_{K}$ is assumed to increase with $x$, and\nin addition, it also shows a qualitative agreement concerning the behavior of\nthe freezing and the Neel temperatures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Mar 2006 18:58:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-25"}
