gy of droplet excitations for\nspin-glasses is also logarithmic at $T_c$, one obtains a logarithmic decay for\nthe mean square correlation function at criticality $\\bar{C^2(r)} \\sim 1/(\\ln r\n)^{\\sigma}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Mar 2006 09:21:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 30 May 2006 08:15:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
